  "title": "만성위장질환, 소화불량",
  "addDate": "2014. 3. 19.",
  "categoryNo": "32",
  "parentCategoryNo": "32",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110187408818",
  "html_size": 208587,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110187408818\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110187408818\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><!--StartFragment--> \r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">여러분들중에 만성 위염, 위,십이지장 궤양, 위하수 등 </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">위장병으로 고생하시는 분들 많으시죠? </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">&#8203;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">&#8203;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">&#8203;<img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140319_177/isuhani_1395206407564iiGcw_JPEG/%C0%A7%C0%E5%C1%FA%C8%AF7.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"406\" height=\"124\" style=\"cursor: pointer; BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 406px; rheight: 124px\" id=\"20140319_177/isuhani_1395206407564iiGcw_JPEG/%C0%A7%C0%E5%C1%FA%C8%AF7.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7AE6DB2')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140319_177/isuhani_1395206407564iiGcw_JPEG/%C0%A7%C0%E5%C1%FA%C8%AF7.jpg?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">&#8203;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">&#8203;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">오늘은 만성 위장질환에 대하여 알아보겠습니다.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">여러 가지 위장질환으로 고생하시는 분들 중에는 </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">스트레스를 많이 받고 신경을 많이 쓰는 사람들이 많습니다. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">또한 식사시간이 불규칙한 사람도 거의 위장병을 갖고 있습니다.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">많은 걱정이나 분노, 자극적인 음식 등도 위장병의 원인이 되지만, </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">부모님으로부터 물려받은 유전이나 체질적인 원인도 많이 작용합니다. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\">&nbsp; </p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\" align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140319_97/isuhani_1395206408817cyD68_JPEG/%C0%A7%C0%E5%C1%FA%C8%AF1.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"299\" height=\"168\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 299px; rheight: 168px\" id=\"20140319_97/isuhani_1395206408817cyD68_JPEG/%C0%A7%C0%E5%C1%FA%C8%AF1.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7AE6DB2')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140319_97/isuhani_1395206408817cyD68_JPEG/%C0%A7%C0%E5%C1%FA%C8%AF1.jpg?type=w3\"></div>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><?xml:namespace prefix = \"o\" /><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) -->&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">일반적으로 속이 쓰리거나 아프고 </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">속이 더부룩하거나 트림이 나며, </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">변비, 설사가 반복되거나, </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">입냄새가 나는 것 등은 위장이 나쁘기 때문입니다. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">이런 경우에는 질환별로 증세를 구분하여 원인에 따라 치료해야 하며 </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">체질에 맞는 치료가 필요합니다.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">&#8203;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">&#8203;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">&#8203;<img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140319_197/isuhani_1395206408284Fn25x_JPEG/%C0%A7%C0%E5%C1%FA%C8%AF4.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"251\" height=\"201\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 251px; rheight: 201px\" id=\"20140319_197/isuhani_1395206408284Fn25x_JPEG/%C0%A7%C0%E5%C1%FA%C8%AF4.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7AE6DB2')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140319_197/isuhani_1395206408284Fn25x_JPEG/%C0%A7%C0%E5%C1%FA%C8%AF4.jpg?type=w3\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\">&nbsp; </p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\">&nbsp;</p><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) -->\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">위장병을 위장의 문제만으로 봐서는 안됩니다.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">몸 전체를 살펴야 하므로 한방치료가 효과적입니다.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\">&nbsp; <!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">한의학에서는 </span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">위장병</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">을 </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">심인(心因)성, 상비(傷脾)성, 간담(肝膽)성으로 </span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">분류</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">합니다.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">&#8203;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">&#8203;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">&#8203;<img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140319_7/isuhani_1395206528335GPqlT_JPEG/images_%289%29.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"275\" height=\"183\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 275px; rheight: 183px\" id=\"20140319_7/isuhani_1395206528335GPqlT_JPEG/images_%289%29.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7AE6DB2')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140319_7/isuhani_1395206528335GPqlT_JPEG/images_%289%29.jpg?type=w3\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">&#8203;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">&#8203;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">첫 번째, 심인성 위장병은 정신적 충격이나 고민으로 생기는 위장병입니다. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">불면증, 가슴 답답함, 불안, 초조, 기억력 감퇴, </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">신경예민, 심장부 통증 등이 동반됩니다. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">특히 심인성일 경우에는 위장뿐 아니라 </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">심장질환까지 복합적으로 나타나거나 </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">혈액순환기능을 저하시키는 경우가 많습니다.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">&#8203;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">&#8203;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">&#8203;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">&#8203;<img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140319_188/isuhani_1395206408533rvjD3_JPEG/%C0%A7%C0%E5%C1%FA%C8%AF2.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"251\" height=\"201\" style=\"cursor: pointer; BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 251px; rheight: 201px\" id=\"20140319_188/isuhani_1395206408533rvjD3_JPEG/%C0%A7%C0%E5%C1%FA%C8%AF2.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7AE6DB2')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140319_188/isuhani_1395206408533rvjD3_JPEG/%C0%A7%C0%E5%C1%FA%C8%AF2.jpg?type=w3\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">&#8203;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\">&nbsp; </p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">두 번째, 상비성 위장병은 비장의 기능이 저하되어 나타나는 것입니다. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">우울한 감정이 지속되거나 </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">깊은 생각을 오래하는 사람에게 주로 나타납니다. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">식욕감퇴, 전신무력감, 피로감, </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">가슴 답답함, 명치부위의 통증, 두통, 어지럼증 등이 동반됩니다.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">&#8203;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">&#8203;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140319_134/isuhani_1395206692201UKzGn_JPEG/%C0%A7%C0%E5%C1%FA%C8%AF8.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"277\" height=\"182\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 277px; rheight: 182px\" id=\"20140319_134/isuhani_1395206692201UKzGn_JPEG/%C0%A7%C0%E5%C1%FA%C8%AF8.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7AE6DB2')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140319_134/isuhani_1395206692201UKzGn_JPEG/%C0%A7%C0%E5%C1%FA%C8%AF8.jpg?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\">&nbsp; </p><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) -->\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">세 번째, 간이나 담기능이 안 좋아도 소화계통에 병이 올 수 있습니다. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">소화불량, 옆구리 통증, 구역질과 함께 </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">안구 충혈, 미열과 오한이 나타날 수 있습니다.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체; mso-fareast-font-family: 굴림체\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">위장병에 많은 영향을 주는 정신적 스트레스에 대해 말씀드리겠습니다.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\">&nbsp; <!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">사람의 일곱 가지 감정, 즉 </span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">기쁨, 노여움, 근심, 생각, </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">슬픔, 놀람, 두려움이 인체의 기순환과 오장육부에 많은 영향을 줍니다.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">지나친 감정은 질병을 일으킬 뿐만 아니라 병의 상태를 변화시키고 악화시킵니다.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\">&nbsp; </p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">신경을 많이 쓰거나 생각을 많이 하면 </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">기혈의 소통이 정체되어 통증과 염증이 유발됩니다.'</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">&#8203;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">&#8203;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\">&nbsp; <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140319_29/isuhani_1395206408397TP8Ht_JPEG/%C0%A7%C0%E5%C1%FA%C8%AF3.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"275\" height=\"183\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 275px; rheight: 183px\" id=\"20140319_29/isuhani_1395206408397TP8Ht_JPEG/%C0%A7%C0%E5%C1%FA%C8%AF3.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7AE6DB2')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140319_29/isuhani_1395206408397TP8Ht_JPEG/%C0%A7%C0%E5%C1%FA%C8%AF3.jpg?type=w3\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">&#8203;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">따라서 울체된 기혈을 소통시키